  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to compare the postoperative pain control in children undergoing&#xD;
      lower abdominal surgeries receiving QL block with those receiving caudal bupivacaine/&#xD;
      neostigmine.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
